<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:20.100 --> 00:00:22.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] It's been
quite a while, Flamme.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:26.820 --> 00:00:29.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000004
00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:23.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bargland, earth control.</b></Default>

c0000005
00:02:26.440 --> 00:02:27.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kanne gasps]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:02:27.980 --> 00:02:29.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000007
00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] I find the young
to be far too hot-blooded.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:02:48.210 --> 00:02:51.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That so-called privilege
is nonsense.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:51.460 --> 00:02:54.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Really?
What makes you say that?</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:54.630 --> 00:02:57.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] You of all people
shouldn't have to ask.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:57.590 --> 00:03:00.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The pursuit of magic stirs
a far greater joy</b></Default>

c0000012
00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:03.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than any good fortune
a spell could possibly bring.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plain and simple.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:03:06.230 --> 00:03:07.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:03:09.770 --> 00:03:11.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] It feels
as if the march of time</b></Default>

c0000016
00:03:11.480 --> 00:03:12.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has become a sprint.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:03:13.400 --> 00:03:14.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE] The apprentice
I brought up on a whim</b></Default>

c0000018
00:03:15.070 --> 00:03:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has already found
an apprentice of her own.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:03:18.490 --> 00:03:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FLAMME]
Meet Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:03:20.910 --> 00:03:22.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An elf, huh?</b></Default>

c0000021
00:03:22.910 --> 00:03:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Must be strong. I like her.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:03:27.540 --> 00:03:29.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If there is any spell
you so desire,</b></Default>

c0000023
00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:31.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just name it and it is yours.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:34.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Any spell I desire?</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:35.130 --> 00:03:36.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Few grimoires have been written</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:38.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that haven't passed
through my hands.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:39.010 --> 00:03:41.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As such, their knowledge
is now mine.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:41.510 --> 00:03:43.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Work that would take
a lifetime,</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:44.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>any spell you want,</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:45.100 --> 00:03:47.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is yours for the taking
if you so crave.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:48.810 --> 00:03:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me what you want,
and I shall grant it to you.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:52.360 --> 00:03:53.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, thanks.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:55.950 --> 00:03:58.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The pursuit of magic brings
far greater joy</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:58.450 --> 00:04:00.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than any spell ever could.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:04:01.370 --> 00:04:02.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Well, Flamme.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:04:03.200 --> 00:04:05.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My initial appraisal was wrong.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:04:05.450 --> 00:04:07.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
There is no fire within her.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:04:07.290 --> 00:04:09.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No blazing ambition.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:04:09.790 --> 00:04:14.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Master, she will someday
defeat the Demon King.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:04:16.340 --> 00:04:18.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's peace that
we're truly after,</b></Default>

c0000041
00:04:18.470 --> 00:04:20.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll need a mage like her
to clear the way.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:04:21.300 --> 00:04:23.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you saying a mage
like me can't?</b></Default>

c0000043
00:04:23.510 --> 00:04:25.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm saying the Demon King</b></Default>

c0000044
00:04:25.100 --> 00:04:27.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>will never be the trophy
of one who seeks battle.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:28.140 --> 00:04:30.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We exist in chaos and fear.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:31.980 --> 00:04:33.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think about it, Master.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:33.860 --> 00:04:35.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FLAMME] Can you even
begin to imagine</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:35.530 --> 00:04:37.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>yourself living
in a world of peace?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:41.320 --> 00:04:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren is a mage who belongs
to a peaceful era.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:44.410 --> 00:04:46.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:51.330 --> 00:04:52.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Good answer.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:53.290 --> 00:04:55.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yours is the mindset
all mages should have.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:57.130 --> 00:04:58.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000054
00:05:04.060 --> 00:05:05.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000055
00:05:09.020 --> 00:05:10.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
Damn it.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:05:10.230 --> 00:05:12.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter what I throw at him,
he won't freeze.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:05:12.810 --> 00:05:15.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The difference between
our mana is too great.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:05:15.980 --> 00:05:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nephtear.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:05:18.360 --> 00:05:19.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[expolsion]</b></Default>

c0000060
00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:26.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
You'll have to try harder.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:05:28.790 --> 00:05:29.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000062
00:05:30.500 --> 00:05:32.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Kanne!
-I'm already on it!</b></Default>

c0000063
00:05:35.710 --> 00:05:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You ladies put on quite
the show earlier.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:05:38.460 --> 00:05:41.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was right in thinking you
gave away most of your tricks.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:05:42.300 --> 00:05:43.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000066
00:05:44.970 --> 00:05:46.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
One mage with relatively</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:46.220 --> 00:05:47.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>non-lethal ice magic.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:48.520 --> 00:05:51.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And one mage
who can't fight without water.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:51.850 --> 00:05:52.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:53.850 --> 00:05:56.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're much more of
an annoyance than a threat.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:56.440 --> 00:05:58.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] "Babysitting"
was the appropriate term.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:06:00.490 --> 00:06:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000073
00:06:05.370 --> 00:06:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] You'll change
your tune soon enough.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:06:07.580 --> 00:06:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you keep casting
such flashy spells,</b></Default>

c0000075
00:06:10.330 --> 00:06:12.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll be out of mana
in minutes at most.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:06:12.830 --> 00:06:13.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000077
00:06:13.750 --> 00:06:16.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] You graduated
from a magic academy, yes?</b></Default>

c0000078
00:06:16.920 --> 00:06:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are the geezers who run
the place</b></Default>

c0000079
00:06:18.670 --> 00:06:20.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>still teaching their students
to fight</b></Default>

c0000080
00:06:20.380 --> 00:06:22.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>overly defensive battles
of attrition?</b></Default>

c0000081
00:06:23.180 --> 00:06:24.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
What are you talking about?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:06:25.090 --> 00:06:26.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
You both could use a lesson</b></Default>

c0000083
00:06:26.510 --> 00:06:27.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the history of magic</b></Default>

c0000084
00:06:29.560 --> 00:06:31.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The defensive spell
we use today</b></Default>

c0000085
00:06:31.230 --> 00:06:33.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was created to combat Zoltraak,</b></Default>

c0000086
00:06:33.350 --> 00:06:36.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and while it is excellent at
defending against magic itself,</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:37.020 --> 00:06:39.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>its effectiveness
against physical objects</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:39.280 --> 00:06:41.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has hardly increased
since its conception.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:42.570 --> 00:06:45.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Naturally, there's a clear
reason why that is the case.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:46.570 --> 00:06:48.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] The barrier created
is enough to defend</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:48.580 --> 00:06:51.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>against the physical attacks
of monsters and warriors.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:52.910 --> 00:06:54.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Defensive magic
will never succeed</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:54.910 --> 00:06:56.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if it's over-engineered.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:56.830 --> 00:07:00.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we seek perfection,
technique grows too complex.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:07:00.710 --> 00:07:02.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] This has a fatal
effect on activation time.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:07:04.010 --> 00:07:07.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The history of magic is rooted
in attack and defense.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:07:07.470 --> 00:07:09.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This explains the trend
for modern attack spells</b></Default>

c0000098
00:07:09.800 --> 00:07:11.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to involve controlling matter
over magic.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:07:13.430 --> 00:07:15.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you understand
what I'm getting at?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:07:18.360 --> 00:07:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000101
00:07:19.730 --> 00:07:21.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Move, Kanne!</b></Default>

c0000102
00:07:24.490 --> 00:07:25.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:07:27.660 --> 00:07:30.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] My strategy
is to overwhelm opponents</b></Default>

c0000104
00:07:30.910 --> 00:07:33.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with high-volume
physical attacks.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:35.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, be smart and stay down.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:07:36.710 --> 00:07:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000107
00:07:39.250 --> 00:07:40.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have I not earned a break?</b></Default>

c0000108
00:07:41.380 --> 00:07:43.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not here to hurt you girls,</b></Default>

c0000109
00:07:43.510 --> 00:07:46.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that can change if you keep
acting like you want to die.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:07:47.760 --> 00:07:50.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Should you really be
approaching us so carelessly?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:07:51.140 --> 00:07:54.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>60% of the human body
is made up of water, after all.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:07:55.140 --> 00:07:56.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what good does that do you?</b></Default>

c0000113
00:07:57.480 --> 00:07:59.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Magic
is the realm of imagination.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:02.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you picture how that
water is distributed</b></Default>

c0000115
00:08:02.900 --> 00:08:04.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>throughout a person's body?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:08:04.730 --> 00:08:07.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you imagine how you would
draw it out and manipulate it?</b></Default>

c0000117
00:08:07.700 --> 00:08:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How you would drive through
the mana that protects me?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:08:10.370 --> 00:08:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A mana greater than yours?</b></Default>

c0000119
00:08:13.870 --> 00:08:15.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Spells can only achieve</b></Default>

c0000120
00:08:15.250 --> 00:08:17.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what you can see
in your mind's eye.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:08:17.580 --> 00:08:18.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And besides,</b></Default>

c0000122
00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if there was water
within reach,</b></Default>

c0000123
00:08:21.090 --> 00:08:23.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a child like you
is not a threat to me.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:08:23.880 --> 00:08:26.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Old men like you
take the fun out of everything,</b></Default>

c0000125
00:08:26.760 --> 00:08:28.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>bluffing included.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:31.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I have figured out
one thing about you.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:08:32.100 --> 00:08:34.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You do think she's a threat.
You're lying.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:08:35.270 --> 00:08:36.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
If you love fighting as much</b></Default>

c0000129
00:08:36.680 --> 00:08:38.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as your lecture indicates,</b></Default>

c0000130
00:08:38.350 --> 00:08:40.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you wouldn't have weakened
one of your opponents</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:42.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by taking her away from water.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:42.770 --> 00:08:44.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're afraid of something.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:48.650 --> 00:08:50.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do I have to fear?</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:51.610 --> 00:08:52.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] The only thing
I need to worry about</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:54.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is putting you kids to sleep.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:57.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] As long as Denken
doesn't lose, that is.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:58.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000138
00:09:11.300 --> 00:09:12.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] At this rate,
our battle will end</b></Default>

c0000139
00:09:12.970 --> 00:09:14.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she exhausts my mana.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:09:16.310 --> 00:09:18.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a bit tough
on my old bones.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:09:19.350 --> 00:09:22.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been an honor, Frieren,
but I need to settle this.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:09:22.690 --> 00:09:23.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Quickly.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:09:26.150 --> 00:09:27.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Waldgose.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:30.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Daosdorg.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:09:31.910 --> 00:09:33.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000146
00:09:37.660 --> 00:09:39.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very subtle.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:09:39.460 --> 00:09:41.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that curmudgeon up to?</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:42.210 --> 00:09:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] It seems that old man
is not one to hold back.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:45.290 --> 00:09:47.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] Think the barrier
will survive this?</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:47.590 --> 00:09:48.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:49.010 --> 00:09:50.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The great mage
Serie's construction</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:52.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is not a thing that needs
to be questioned.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:53.300 --> 00:09:55.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] It cannot be destroyed
by brute force.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:56.560 --> 00:09:58.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. Well, that's good.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:59.680 --> 00:10:01.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, since last night,</b></Default>

c0000156
00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:03.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>someone has been analyzing
the barrier.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:10:03.730 --> 00:10:04.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000158
00:10:05.810 --> 00:10:07.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would they do that?</b></Default>

c0000159
00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:08.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
I don't know.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:10:09.070 --> 00:10:11.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] In any case,
they're wasting their time.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:10:11.740 --> 00:10:13.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think there's a mage
in this world</b></Default>

c0000162
00:10:13.490 --> 00:10:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>more powerful than Serie?</b></Default>

c0000163
00:10:18.540 --> 00:10:19.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

c0000164
00:10:23.670 --> 00:10:24.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000165
00:10:24.870 --> 00:10:26.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Catastravia.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:30.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000167
00:10:35.510 --> 00:10:37.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
A counterattack? Impossible.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:10:37.760 --> 00:10:39.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My arrows of light
were launched</b></Default>

c0000169
00:10:39.220 --> 00:10:41.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a continuous barrage.
There was no opening!</b></Default>

c0000170
00:10:47.770 --> 00:10:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000171
00:10:59.540 --> 00:11:03.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] I'm out of mana.
So, this is the end.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:11:03.830 --> 00:11:05.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't believe it.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:11:05.330 --> 00:11:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was able to best me</b></Default>

c0000174
00:11:06.830 --> 00:11:09.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using only the most basic
of combat spells.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:11:10.750 --> 00:11:12.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This felt no different from
a training match</b></Default>

c0000176
00:11:12.880 --> 00:11:15.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>between a master
and their apprentice.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:11:17.140 --> 00:11:18.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm surprised.</b></Default>

c0000178
00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:20.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how far I've come,</b></Default>

c0000179
00:11:20.220 --> 00:11:22.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there is still someone
above me.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:24.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me where your teammate
Laufen is.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:26.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And don't pretend
you don't know.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:11:27.270 --> 00:11:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to take back
our Stille.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:11:30.270 --> 00:11:31.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
If you were in my position,</b></Default>

c0000184
00:11:31.730 --> 00:11:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how do you suppose
you would answer that demand?</b></Default>

c0000185
00:11:35.070 --> 00:11:36.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Good point.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:11:37.620 --> 00:11:39.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000187
00:11:40.870 --> 00:11:42.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000188
00:11:46.500 --> 00:11:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Laufen?</b></Default>

c0000189
00:11:47.960 --> 00:11:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've been hiding nearby,
haven't you?</b></Default>

c0000190
00:11:50.290 --> 00:11:52.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I need you
to bring me the Stille.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:11:53.630 --> 00:11:56.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you don't,
I will kill Denken.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:11:57.130 --> 00:11:58.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Do not listen to her, Laufen.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:11:59.300 --> 00:12:01.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She doesn't intend to kill me.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:12:01.260 --> 00:12:02.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can tell that much.</b></Default>

c0000195
00:12:02.760 --> 00:12:04.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN] She's a much
better mage than I am.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:12:04.970 --> 00:12:06.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even better than Richter.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:12:06.890 --> 00:12:08.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she can beat the old man,</b></Default>

c0000198
00:12:08.140 --> 00:12:10.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she could pummel the both of us
in an instant.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:12:10.650 --> 00:12:12.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But she's letting
her guard down.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:12:12.360 --> 00:12:14.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's not maintaining
contact with him.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:12:14.650 --> 00:12:16.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Whatever you do,
don't use Jilwer.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:12:16.950 --> 00:12:19.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you move,
our failure is sealed.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:12:19.570 --> 00:12:22.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Release any mana at all,
and she will detect you.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:12:22.620 --> 00:12:23.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN]
From this distance,</b></Default>

c0000205
00:12:23.910 --> 00:12:25.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can retrieve him quickly
and flee!</b></Default>

c0000206
00:12:26.330 --> 00:12:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Stay where you are.
It's a trap.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:12:28.580 --> 00:12:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You leave me no choice.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:12:30.670 --> 00:12:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please know this doesn't
bring me any joy.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:12:33.210 --> 00:12:34.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Laufen gasps]</b></Default>

c0000210
00:12:35.380 --> 00:12:36.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
There you are.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:12:37.010 --> 00:12:38.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000212
00:12:39.130 --> 00:12:40.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
You fool.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:12:41.390 --> 00:12:42.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[bird chirping]</b></Default>

c0000214
00:12:43.850 --> 00:12:45.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You knew she wouldn't kill me.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:12:45.600 --> 00:12:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you had any experience,
you would have trusted in that.</b></Default>

c0000216
00:12:49.350 --> 00:12:50.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN]
She may not have killed you,</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:51.230 --> 00:12:53.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she was obviously going to
hurt you if I didn't come out.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
And when we won,</b></Default>

c0000219
00:12:55.690 --> 00:12:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the pain would
soon be forgotten.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:12:57.860 --> 00:12:59.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000221
00:12:59.110 --> 00:13:00.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't get it.
Why is someone like you</b></Default>

c0000222
00:13:01.030 --> 00:13:03.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so desperate to be
a first-class mage, anyway?</b></Default>

c0000223
00:13:03.580 --> 00:13:05.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're wealthy and powerful.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:13:05.160 --> 00:13:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What could this bring you
that you don't already have?</b></Default>

c0000225
00:13:13.130 --> 00:13:15.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] My homeland
is located out in the depths</b></Default>

c0000226
00:13:15.290 --> 00:13:16.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Northern Plateau.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:13:17.510 --> 00:13:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With the increase in
demon activity,</b></Default>

c0000228
00:13:19.680 --> 00:13:22.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only first-class mages
can enter the area now.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:13:23.800 --> 00:13:26.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to visit a grave
I haven't been to in a while.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:13:27.350 --> 00:13:28.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plain and simple.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:13:30.600 --> 00:13:33.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you think you should go
help your party members?</b></Default>

c0000232
00:13:34.270 --> 00:13:37.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a decent chance
you may already be too late.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:13:38.030 --> 00:13:40.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Richter will surely dispose
of those children</b></Default>

c0000234
00:13:40.490 --> 00:13:42.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>before he comes down
to challenge you.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:13:42.990 --> 00:13:45.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's capable of a harsh
pragmatism</b></Default>

c0000236
00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that many of us are not.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:47.120 --> 00:13:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My party will be just fine.
In fact, they will win.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:50.330 --> 00:13:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:52.750 --> 00:13:55.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I just finished
analyzing the barrier.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:57.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm...</b></Default>

c0000241
00:13:57.880 --> 00:14:00.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] I wasn't expecting
Denken to lose.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:02.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry, ladies.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:14:03.260 --> 00:14:05.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suddenly have more
important things to do</b></Default>

c0000244
00:14:05.550 --> 00:14:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than babysit.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:14:08.890 --> 00:14:10.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000246
00:14:25.570 --> 00:14:27.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000247
00:14:31.910 --> 00:14:33.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With his boss down,
he's actually</b></Default>

c0000248
00:14:33.420 --> 00:14:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>trying to kill us.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:14:34.920 --> 00:14:36.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] I don't think
we'll last a full minute.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:14:37.880 --> 00:14:40.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're done
"analyzing the barrier?"</b></Default>

c0000251
00:14:40.590 --> 00:14:42.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What does that even mean?</b></Default>

c0000252
00:14:43.800 --> 00:14:46.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] [gasps]
Wait, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:14:46.850 --> 00:14:48.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't tell me
you're planning to...</b></Default>

c0000254
00:14:49.310 --> 00:14:50.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000255
00:14:58.360 --> 00:14:59.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
Genau.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:15:00.020 --> 00:15:03.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It will never fracture.
That much I'm sure of.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:15:03.610 --> 00:15:06.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] Not even if the world
were turned upside down.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:15:07.870 --> 00:15:09.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000259
00:15:13.160 --> 00:15:14.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then "never" is here.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:15:18.170 --> 00:15:19.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000261
00:15:21.590 --> 00:15:22.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU]
Sense?</b></Default>

c0000262
00:15:22.670 --> 00:15:25.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need you to tell me
just who that elf is.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:15:26.840 --> 00:15:29.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE] According to the list
of test-takers,</b></Default>

c0000264
00:15:29.300 --> 00:15:30.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>her name is Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:15:31.140 --> 00:15:32.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU]
That's the name of the mage</b></Default>

c0000266
00:15:32.520 --> 00:15:34.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who traveled with the party
of Heroes.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:15:34.690 --> 00:15:35.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SENSE]
Not only that,</b></Default>

c0000268
00:15:35.810 --> 00:15:38.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she was carrying
a holy emblem with her.</b></Default>

c0000269
00:15:38.610 --> 00:15:41.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU] The last
great mage is before us.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:15:42.110 --> 00:15:44.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SERIE]
Now you've done it, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:15:44.820 --> 00:15:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been a thousand years,
and this is how you say hello?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:15:49.780 --> 00:15:52.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've reminded me
why I will never retire.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:15:53.160 --> 00:15:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For in the world of magic,</b></Default>

c0000274
00:15:54.830 --> 00:15:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>creation itself can be
turned upside down.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:15:58.500 --> 00:15:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
I didn't take you for the type</b></Default>

c0000276
00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:02.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to break the games
you cannot win.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:16:02.250 --> 00:16:04.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why'd you destroy the barrier?</b></Default>

c0000278
00:16:04.420 --> 00:16:06.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Largely because
I felt sorry for Kanne.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:16:07.050 --> 00:16:09.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone should have access
to their magic.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:16:09.930 --> 00:16:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] She's the young mage
who manipulates water, yes?</b></Default>

c0000281
00:16:13.640 --> 00:16:15.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Magic's the realm
of imagination.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:16:16.310 --> 00:16:17.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Can you picture a world</b></Default>

c0000283
00:16:17.390 --> 00:16:19.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in which you'd win a fight
against a mage</b></Default>

c0000284
00:16:19.190 --> 00:16:20.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who can control the rain?
[rain splattering]</b></Default>

c0000285
00:16:21.610 --> 00:16:23.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know that I, for one,
surely cannot.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:16:24.650 --> 00:16:26.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] And I doubt your
friend Richter can, either.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:16:27.490 --> 00:16:28.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The barrier's down.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:16:29.780 --> 00:16:31.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
What happened?</b></Default>

c0000289
00:16:31.530 --> 00:16:32.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE]
It's raining.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:16:33.030 --> 00:16:35.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] No. This is not the
time to assess the situation.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:16:36.080 --> 00:16:37.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must finish them off imme--</b></Default>

c0000292
00:16:38.330 --> 00:16:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all that talk,
you gave us an opening.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:16:41.130 --> 00:16:43.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE] Your panic
is disrupting your mana.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:16:43.210 --> 00:16:44.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] You've only
bought yourselves time!</b></Default>

c0000295
00:16:45.340 --> 00:16:47.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

c0000296
00:16:48.220 --> 00:16:49.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
Now it makes sense.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:16:50.470 --> 00:16:52.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand the reason
you were too scared</b></Default>

c0000298
00:16:52.300 --> 00:16:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fight us by the water.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:16:54.930 --> 00:16:56.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
This is the perfect example</b></Default>

c0000300
00:16:56.350 --> 00:16:58.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the high-volume
physical attacks</b></Default>

c0000301
00:16:58.100 --> 00:17:00.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you mentioned being hard
to defend against.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:17:00.980 --> 00:17:03.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lawine, don't let him escape.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:17:04.110 --> 00:17:05.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Reamstroha!</b></Default>

c0000304
00:17:09.490 --> 00:17:12.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] You realize there's
nowhere for me to escape to.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:17:14.660 --> 00:17:17.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is exactly
why I hate the water.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:17:19.580 --> 00:17:21.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water crashing]</b></Default>

c0000307
00:17:27.260 --> 00:17:29.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water burbling]</b></Default>

c0000308
00:17:31.510 --> 00:17:33.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You claimed the victory, then.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:17:33.510 --> 00:17:35.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's move before we rejoice.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:17:35.810 --> 00:17:37.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have two hours until sunset.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:17:37.810 --> 00:17:39.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Conceal your mana until then.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:17:40.060 --> 00:17:42.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I don't have
any mana left to conceal.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:17:42.900 --> 00:17:44.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. Great work, you two.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:17:45.110 --> 00:17:46.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000315
00:17:46.190 --> 00:17:47.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't pat me.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:17:51.110 --> 00:17:52.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
Sorry.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:17:53.620 --> 00:17:55.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
It was inevitable.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:18:00.580 --> 00:18:03.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Denken and I are
both completely out of mana.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:18:05.290 --> 00:18:07.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are only two hours left,</b></Default>

c0000320
00:18:07.170 --> 00:18:09.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which means we're as good
as finished.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:18:10.260 --> 00:18:11.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:18:12.090 --> 00:18:14.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Laufen.
Can you dispel the binding?</b></Default>

c0000323
00:18:15.180 --> 00:18:16.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN]
You have to be kidding.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:18:16.760 --> 00:18:18.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's enough mana here
to hold back a dragon.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:18:20.020 --> 00:18:21.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Let's get creative, then.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:18:21.690 --> 00:18:23.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fell the tree.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:18:23.310 --> 00:18:24.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000328
00:18:25.560 --> 00:18:27.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tree crashing]</b></Default>

c0000329
00:18:28.900 --> 00:18:30.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000330
00:18:31.570 --> 00:18:33.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] Denken.
There's nothing we can do.</b></Default>

c0000331
00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:35.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm running so low on mana</b></Default>

c0000332
00:18:35.700 --> 00:18:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that it's safe to say using
Jilwer is out of the question.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:18:39.490 --> 00:18:41.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Come, now. Both of you.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:18:41.540 --> 00:18:43.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you suppose
an imperial mage would do</b></Default>

c0000335
00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a situation like this?</b></Default>

c0000336
00:18:46.500 --> 00:18:49.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how ugly it may be,
we fight until the end.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:18:51.340 --> 00:18:54.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's see if we can pick up
on the trails of other parties</b></Default>

c0000338
00:18:54.180 --> 00:18:55.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and track them down.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:18:57.430 --> 00:19:01.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Fern, are you aware
of how deeply boring you are?</b></Default>

c0000340
00:19:04.190 --> 00:19:07.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've only ever seen you cast
the most basic of spells.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:19:07.190 --> 00:19:09.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should take your complaints
to Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:19:11.110 --> 00:19:13.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so strange to me
that mysterious elf lady</b></Default>

c0000343
00:19:13.570 --> 00:19:14.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is your master.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL]
Speaking of, it's her fault</b></Default>

c0000345
00:19:18.830 --> 00:19:20.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're soaking wet right now.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:19:20.490 --> 00:19:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make sure that you give her
an earful.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:19:23.080 --> 00:19:24.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Trust me, I intend to.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:19:26.250 --> 00:19:28.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I have cast
interesting spells.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:19:28.540 --> 00:19:30.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She only limits my combat.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:19:30.750 --> 00:19:32.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah, that bird-catching
spell you used</b></Default>

c0000351
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is actually impressive.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:37.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What other exciting stuff
are you sitting on?</b></Default>

c0000353
00:19:37.550 --> 00:19:39.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, um...</b></Default>

c0000354
00:19:39.510 --> 00:19:42.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have a spell that allows you
to see through clothes.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:19:42.930 --> 00:19:44.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I am not going to cast it.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:19:45.600 --> 00:19:46.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wise decision.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:19:47.020 --> 00:19:49.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>While I hate to interrupt
pleasant conversation,</b></Default>

c0000358
00:19:49.770 --> 00:19:51.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>perhaps we shouldn't reveal
too many</b></Default>

c0000359
00:19:51.230 --> 00:19:52.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of our tricks just yet.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:19:53.230 --> 00:19:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAND]
From the second test onward,</b></Default>

c0000361
00:19:55.030 --> 00:19:56.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we'll be competing
against one another.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:19:57.700 --> 00:19:59.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm. You make a good point.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:20:00.200 --> 00:20:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[UBEL] [chuckling]
I'm sorry.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:20:02.580 --> 00:20:04.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Teamwork's
not your strong suit,</b></Default>

c0000365
00:20:04.120 --> 00:20:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you could've opened up
to us a little bit, four-eyes.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:20:11.630 --> 00:20:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
There they are.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:14.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That must be the party
that fled.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:20:15.460 --> 00:20:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The corpse of their third
member is just up the road.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:20:18.890 --> 00:20:21.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even though there's no way
for them to pass the exam,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:20:21.390 --> 00:20:24.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they're holding tight
to their Stille all the same.</b></Default>

c0000371
00:20:28.640 --> 00:20:30.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, should we try to
negotiate with them, then?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:20:31.400 --> 00:20:32.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
They wouldn't cooperate.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:20:32.940 --> 00:20:35.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I were in their position,
nothing would sway me.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:20:35.650 --> 00:20:37.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd refuse even money.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:20:38.280 --> 00:20:39.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAUFEN]
Why's that?</b></Default>

c0000376
00:20:39.740 --> 00:20:41.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] Because
it wouldn't sit right with me.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:20:42.200 --> 00:20:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those men are past
the point of logic.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:20:44.620 --> 00:20:45.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER]
Mm.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:20:46.040 --> 00:20:47.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
You will wait here, Laufen.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:20:47.830 --> 00:20:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you see an opportunity,
take their Stille.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:20:50.210 --> 00:20:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Richter, you come with me.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:20:53.380 --> 00:20:55.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But what is our plan?</b></Default>

c0000383
00:20:57.090 --> 00:20:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000384
00:21:05.720 --> 00:21:08.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Approaching them
head-on won't work.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:10.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Both of us are fully depleted
of mana.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:21:11.730 --> 00:21:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN]
Use your head for a moment.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:21:14.820 --> 00:21:17.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They are clearly
in the same boat.</b></Default>

c0000388
00:21:26.240 --> 00:21:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Prepare yourself.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:21:28.540 --> 00:21:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clothes rustling]</b></Default>

c0000390
00:21:31.790 --> 00:21:34.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're all men here,
are we not?</b></Default>

c0000391
00:21:35.460 --> 00:21:37.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on. You're joking.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:21:39.800 --> 00:21:44.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] We will
settle this with our fists!</b></Default>

c0000393
00:21:46.140 --> 00:21:49.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000394
00:22:10.580 --> 00:22:12.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GENAU]
It is time.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:22:13.670 --> 00:22:15.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now that the sun has set,</b></Default>

c0000396
00:22:15.330 --> 00:22:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the first test
is officially over.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:22:17.710 --> 00:22:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Six parties
and eighteen individuals remain</b></Default>

c0000398
00:22:20.630 --> 00:22:22.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and will move
to the next trial.</b></Default>

c0000399
00:22:22.970 --> 00:22:25.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The second test will take place
in three days.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:22:25.970 --> 00:22:28.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You will be informed
of the details later.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:22:28.850 --> 00:22:30.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is all. You're dismissed.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:22:34.270 --> 00:22:35.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
It's only been two days</b></Default>

c0000403
00:22:35.650 --> 00:22:37.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since they headed off
for the exam.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:40.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can stay up as late
as I want,</b></Default>

c0000405
00:22:40.570 --> 00:22:42.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and Fern isn't around
to get mad at me.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:22:42.990 --> 00:22:45.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so happy that
it's almost frightening.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:22:46.410 --> 00:22:47.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE BARTENDER 21A]
Bless you, buddy.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:22:47.490 --> 00:22:49.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds like
you've been through it.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:24:20.250 --> 00:24:22.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[LAUFEN] I'm not sharing.
-Don't talk about that.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:24:22.670 --> 00:24:24.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KANNE] You're even
more spoiled than me.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:24:24.300 --> 00:24:26.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[DENKEN] You must eat
your vegetables, too.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:24:26.510 --> 00:24:27.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RICHTER] We're no longer
party members.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:24:27.970 --> 00:24:29.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LAWINE]
Past allies are future enemies.</b></Default>

